Package: pesco
Type: Package
Title: Data fusion for air quality data
Version: 0.3.2
Date: 2016-10-04
Author: Lucia Paci, Giovanni Bonafe'
Maintainer: G.Bonafe' <gbonafe@arpa.emr.it>
Imports: geoR, akima, fields, caTools, ncdf4, timeDate, chron
Description: PESCO stands for Post-processing and Evaluation with Statistical methods of a Chemistry-transport-model Output. Patched by LaMMMA Francesca Guarnieri for R 3.5.2 .The package provides functions to perform data fusion for air quality data, correcting the output of a deterministic CTM with observed data, with a Trans-Gaussian Kriging approach.
License: GPL-2
